; MOUSE.DEF - module definition para Windows 1.x
; AUTO-GENERATED desde MOUSE.DRV (NE entry/relocation tables)

LIBRARY     MOUSE
DESCRIPTION 'Microsoft Mouse (Bus/Serial)'
